@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ffxoau(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.85 * wp.cos(wp.cos(tmp + 0.31)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.99)) / wp.exp((tmp + 0.34 - v0 + 0.90)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v2 + 0.10) + (v0 + 0.70 / v1 + 0.43)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v1 + 0.33) / (v0 + 0.30 + v1 + 0.60)) / (tmp - (v2 + 0.42 / v0 + 0.73)))
    v0 = wp.sin(v0)
    data[tid] = v0
